- The ranking is based on annual revenue, with the highest revenue accounts ranked first;
- Recent activity includes the count of update and delete operations on the accounts.

sql:
SELECT COUNT(*) 
FROM accounts 
WHERE annual_revenue > (SELECT AVG(annual_revenue) FROM accounts WHERE type = 'Individual');

